        ],
        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "Scott/Sally Devire: Wandering Malkavian with Obsession: Justice, (possibly delusions of grandeur,) and a white knight complex. Highly skilled in melee and hand to hand combat. In life, they were a nerd, obsessed with either samurai movies or Arthurian lore. It ingrained in them a deep seated sense of ethics, and an unshakable code of honor and justice. A Longtime student in many different fields, they changed their course of study often, and Never having accomplished much before their death in the mid seventies, being embraced opened an entirely new Avenue for them. Finally, using their improved Vampire bodies, they could make a difference in the world.  Right the wrongs, and punish the wicked. There is a society of creatures like them, and the weak must be protected to ensure they are not overly abused. They learned more, taking the time to hone their physical and mental prowess, educating themselves in things from combat to the arts and music, in order to emulate the wandering Ronin, or Knight Errants of their youth. They covet the position of Archon, which seem to be handmade for them. But that's a Very lofty position.  In the meantime, they've decided to start small, and aim for Sheriff, or Scourge. So far, they haven’t managed to stay in one place too long, (No one ever seems to appreciate their assistance for some reason,) but Los Angeles is a big city with hundreds of problems, surely they are needed here? Their days are plagued with nightmares about the people and causes they've failed in the past, and their nights by visions of a terrible future they're certain can be prevented if they can hold to their ideals."
        ],
